# Pin LF everywhere. The provenance gate asserts a fresh `make fixtures` is
# byte-identical to the committed artifacts; CRLF<->LF conversion across the
# Windows author and the Linux CI runner would break that byte-equality. Force LF
# for all text so the bytes are platform-independent.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.jsonl text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
*.py text eol=lf
